      "comment": "DREAM LINKIN (1) showed little early speed at her last couple, the latest finishing sixth (19.78) in a Grade 5 at Bulli. Better than last start and worth following up. SUPER SASSY (8) jumped from out wide and was game in defeat last start when a one length third (19.53) behind Huggett at Bulli. Expected to be in this for a long way. BLAZING CASH (2) flew the lids from the middle with a slick turn of foot and stuck on well despite missing the frame, finishing fifth over 365m Nowra in 21.14. The form from his last run stacks up well. Cannot be taken lightly. HIBIKI BLUE (7) comes into calculations after placing most recently.",
